eader_party            = \n| leader_title            = [[City manager]]\n| leader_name             = Risto Laurikainen\n| unit_pref               = Metric<!-- or US or UK -->\n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_total_km2          = 364.76\n| area_land_km2           = 342.77\n| area_water_km2          = 21.99\n| area_rank               = [[List of Finnish municipalities by area|250th]]\n| area_note               = \n| elevation_footnotes     = \n| elevation_m             = \n| population_footnotes    = \n| population_total        = 2157\n| population_as_of        = 2003\n| population_rank         = [[List of Finnish municipalities by population|341st]]\n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| population_demonym      = \n| population_note         = +0.1 % change\n| blank_name              = Official [[language]]s \n| blank_info              = [[Finnish language|Finnish]]\n| blank1_name             = [[Urbanisation]]\n| blank1_info             = 45.4%\n| blank2_name             = [[Unemployment]] rate\n| blank2_info             = 12.7%\n| blank3_name             = [[K\u00f6ppen climate classification|Climate]]\n| blank3_info             = [[Subarctic climate|Dfc]]\n| timezone                = [[Eastern European Time|EET]]\n| utc_offset              = +2\n| timezone_DST            = [[Eastern European Summer Time|EEST]]\n| utc_offset_DST          = +3\n| postal_code_type        = \n| postal_code             = \n| area_code_type          = \n| area_code               = \n| website                 = [http://www.ylane.fi/ www.ylane.fi]\n| footnotes               = \n}}\n\n'''Yl\u00e4ne''' ({{IPA-fi|\u02c8yl\u00e6ne}}) is a [[List of former municipalities of Finland|former municipality]] of [[Finland]]. It was consolidated to [[P\u00f6yty\u00e4]] on 1 January 2009.\n\nIt is located in the [[provinces of Finland|province]] of [[Western Finland]] and is part of the [[Southwest Finland]] [[regions of Finland|region]]. The municipality had a population of 2,119 (2004-12-31) and covered an area of 364.76&nbsp;km\u00b2 of which 21.99&nbsp;km\u00b2 is water. The [[population density]] was 6.18 inhabitants per km\u00b2.\n\nThe municipality was unilingually [[Finnish language|Finnish]].\n\n==External links==\n[[File:Yl\u00e4ne village.JPG|thumb|left|250px|The village of Yl\u00e4ne in December 2012.]]\n{{commonscat-inline|Yl\u00e4ne}}\n*[http://www.p\u00f6yty\u00e4.fi/ P\u00f6yty\u00e4] \u2013 Official website {{in lang|fi}}\n\n{{FinlandProper}}\n\n{{coord|60|52|45|N|22|24|40|E|region:FI_type:city(2119)_scale:50000|display=title}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ylane}}\n[[Category:Former municipalities of Finland]]\n[[Category:Populated places disestablished in 2009]]\n[[Category:2009 disestablishments in Finland]]\n{{WesternFinland-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n| name                    = Yl\u00e4ne\n| official_name           = {{lang|fi|Yl\u00e4neen kunta}}<br />{{lang|sv|Yl\u00e4ne kommun}}\n| native_name             = <!-- if different from name -->\n| native_name_lang        = <!-- ISO 639-2 code. If more than one, use {{lang}} instead  -->\n| settlement_type         = [[Municipalities of Finland|Former municipality]]\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| image_flag              = \n| flag_alt                = \n| image_seal              = \n| seal_alt                = \n| image_shield            = Yl\u00e4ne.vaakuna.svg\n| shield_alt              = \n| nickname                = \n| motto                   = \n| image_map               = Yl\u00e4ne.sijainti.suomi.2008.svg\n| map_alt                 = \n| map_caption             = \n| pushpin_map             = <!-- Finland -->\n| pushpin_label_position  = right\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location within Finland\n| coordinates             = \n| coor_pinpoint           = \n| coordinates_footnotes   